@kool7d note that your comment has blocked registration for almost one week.  As written in _all_ pull requests here

> If you want to prevent this pull request from being auto-merged, simply leave a comment. If you want to post a comment without blocking auto-merging, you must include the text [noblock] in your comment.

_**All**_ comments _**must**_ have `[noblock]` in order for automerge to work.  If you don't want to block your own pull requests you have to add `[noblock]` to your messages, or more simply not comment at all
